of this work to the\nliterature is the affirmation that, in applications, the modified additive\ncorrelation sums, which are easier to handle than the original correlation\nsums, are sufficient.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 24 Feb 2023 18:50:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-27"}
